020-07-01T09:30:51.000Z","msg":"2毛"},{"pid":"d2396d6504fec7bd3a621468864259f23739547e","tid":2088664,"uid":329551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:33:05.000Z","msg":"民主黨話嘅係<br />\n（美國/一個國家）有國安法無問題，只要政權唔係獨裁。<br />\n（美國/一個國家）有國歌法無問題，因為係定義標準，無刑事責任。<br />\n共產黨獨裁，佢哋嘅國安法民主黨講明唔可以接受。<br />\n共產黨想定嘅國歌法有刑事責任，民主黨講明唔可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n班律師講嘢有邏輯，但係分析太多，經常被熱狗城班仆街特登斷章取義明屈。熱狗城啲『理據』仲衰過內容農場啲假新聞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上熱狗城班仆街最叻將人哋講嘅嘢翦翦貼貼，切到佢哋想聽嘅說話，然後就屈人地講過。班律師講咁多廢話，好容易被熱狗城儲齊要用嘅Soundbite去剪接合成。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ada9430230229a94cd44b4936732bfa1183839a","tid":2088664,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:33:10.000Z","msg":"起底 拉"},{"pid":"e0d4b4c425d9b11be95624e37b9cb105e54be672","tid":2088664,"uid":217822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"07ac35911597d3120eaf389c1ddd618276f6bdb9","tid":2088664,"uid":106604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7fa0e4e3a27593b7abf8120acce8aae0088cb63e","tid":2088664,"uid":217822,"like":2,"dislike":38,"score":-36,"quote":{"pid":"959e46c1d897f14923ce98ae3b0ea9a1321d6456","tid":2088664,"uid":134071,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:00:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2018-12-17既文章</span>"},"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"好耐?2018 12已經抗爭左半年<br />\n希望契媽回應下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:30:30.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有啲柒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"無18年嘅妥協國歌法都立唔到"},{"pid":"4590c9615ef5d50c1bc2042a9604100d61681d89","tid":2088664,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:33:41.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets